      <title>英国 Indeed 招聘信息中提供的薪酬自 1 月份以来上涨最多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uk-pay-offered-in-indeed-job-postings-rises-most-since-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国企业在招聘岗位上以自一月份以来最快的速度上调工资，这成为持续通胀压力的一个来源，可能会使降息变得复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uk-pay-offered-in-indeed-job-postings-rises-most-since-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
